{"tid":648388,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"日本生命教育 學生親自孵化小雞 養育 最後親手屠宰煮黎食 學生喊爆猛講「對唔住」","createTime":"2018-04-30T15:48:40.000Z","updateTime":"2018-04-30T23:48:02.000Z","uid":48083,"like":17,"dislike":5,"uniUserReply":17,"replies":[{"pid":"7613df8532d80d07a7b115bdc3a31daa9a4a07c0","tid":648388,"uid":48083,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:48:40.000Z","msg":"條片值得一睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180430/58134953\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58134953&d=SoHoN3jx8HdMuib1ab2rs2Mi7htmHpjw5c1LyB4FCwE%3D&h=e788a798\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2Farticle%2F20180430%2F58134953&h=62466d4a\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.appledaily.com/international/realtime/article/20180430/58134953</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/04/30/234830_3db76dc126d2c69699138f8773a95e48.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F04%2F30%2F234830_3db76dc126d2c69699138f8773a95e48.png&h=b703b98d&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n平時大塊大塊吃肉，很少想到那來自生命，日本有高中在課程中加入「生命教育」，安排學生親手孵化小雞，養大後還要親手屠宰煮成餐桌上的食物，過程中很多女生不捨淚流滿面，網民反應則兩極，有人認為此後會更珍惜肉食，也有人擔心會留下陰影，令學生變得冷血。<br />\n<br />\n推行此「生命教育」的是島根巿出雲農林高等學校，課程一開始，學生先在雞蛋上寫上名字，並把雞蛋放進孵化器中。等待小雞孵化之後，學生開始正式養育牠們，她們要確認培育箱溫度和濕度、更換飲用水、紀錄雞隻成長。<br />\n<br />\n半年過去，不少學生均對小雞培養出感情，但殘忍的時刻也來臨了，課程尾聲他們要學習如何宰殺雞隻，教師高橋知廣說：「最重要的是讓牠們盡早結束痛苦。」許多學生在觀看示範過程時已淚流滿面，有學生互相擁抱痛哭，不捨的心情溢於言表。<br />\n<br />\n影片中可見，在老師的指導下，學生們兩人一組宰殺小雞，幾乎所有學生都在淌淚，一名女學生流著淚、啜泣對雞隻不斷說「對不起」。<br />\n<br />\n接下來學生親手處理、烹調雞肉。當所有學生坐在教室裡，心懷感恩的吃掉桌上擺放著的一盤雞肉之後，這門課程也正式結束。教師高橋知廣認為，「在養育生命到最後把牠們吃掉的這個過程中，讓學生們學到生命的重要」。<br />\n<br />\n台灣《自由時報》/《東森新聞》"},{"pid":"726c796e8f0276842b95a41126e7a21a4c4516e6","tid":648388,"uid":94906,"like":7,"dislike":0,"score":7,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:50:21.000Z","msg":"銀之匙<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/oh.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"50d8a9d87a57e6b8f333746dab5c0ecbc596b3f0","tid":648388,"uid":143597,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:52:30.000Z","msg":"日本又贏<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"8055ab5405d81c481eda36094ed73749a6b82ef5","tid":648388,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"啲架妹仔真係喊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見好心痛<br />\n好想安慰佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7d87db4ad2dbd34e8daaba71a1ac66c628d42a51","tid":648388,"uid":149925,"like":2,"dislike":11,"score":-9,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:53:46.000Z","msg":"我就係因為咁由細到大唔食白切雞，係大咗先可以食番小小"},{"pid":"29a69c7bf324c7ee07dbce5cd90962646545a0b8","tid":648388,"uid":58958,"like":8,"dislike":0,"score":8,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T16:32:44.000Z","msg":"我覺得幾好，更識得感恩珍惜食物"},{"pid":"e58ed507b73ba394e5030b9a0c8e9f1ee0591f36","tid":648388,"uid":136662,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"quote":{"pid":"8055ab5405d81c481eda36094ed73749a6b82ef5","tid":648388,"uid":48083,"like":1,"dislike":5,"score":-4,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-04-30T15:53:32.000Z","msg":"啲架妹仔真係喊哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/23.png\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n睇見好心痛<br />\n好想安慰佢哋<img src=\"/assets/faces/lomoji/19